54
00:04:23,760 --> 00:04:24,720
Is that dad?

55
00:04:25,090 --> 00:04:27,770
Look, I know this is hard
for you to understand. Just...

56
00:04:28,080 --> 00:04:30,010
You're gonna have
to trust me on this.

57
