73
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:09,130
You can't be any part of it.

74
00:05:09,260 --> 00:05:10,200
Why not?

75
00:05:10,400 --> 00:05:11,120
Give me the phone.

76
00:05:11,150 --> 00:05:13,080
Listen, Sammy, that's why I'm calling.

77
00:05:13,580 --> 00:05:15,950
You and your brother, you've got
to stop looking for me.

78
00:05:16,110 --> 00:05:18,330
All right now, I need you
to write down these names.

79
00:05:18,410 --> 00:05:19,410
Names?

80
00:05:19,950 --> 00:05:21,390
What names, dad? Wha...

81
00:05:22,100 --> 00:05:24,030
Talk to me. Tell me what's going on.

82
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:26,080
Look, we don't have time
for this.

83
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:28,170
This is bigger than you think.
They're everywhere.

84
00:05:28,510 --> 00:05:30,800
Even us talking right now, it's not safe.

85
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:31,650
No.

86
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:32,840
All right?

87
00:05:32,910 --> 00:05:33,540
No way.

88
00:05:33,620 --> 00:05:34,460
Give me the phone.

89
00:05:34,570 --> 00:05:35,940
I've given you an order.

90
00:05:36,170 --> 00:05:38,420
Now, you stop following me,
and you do your job.

91
00:05:38,500 --> 00:05:39,750
You understand me?

92
00:05:40,420 --> 00:05:41,720
Now take down these names.

93
00:05:42,450 --> 00:05:43,360
Dad,

94
00:05:43,510 --> 00:05:45,040
