before another couple vanishes?

115
00:06:37,930 --> 00:06:38,870
Yahtzee.

116
00:06:40,170 --> 00:06:42,630
Can you imagine putting together a pattern like this?

117
00:06:42,750 --> 00:06:44,730
The different obits dad had to go through,

118
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:45,980
the man's a master.

119
00:06:50,840 --> 00:06:52,050
What are you doing?

120
00:06:53,500 --> 00:06:54,950
We're not going to Indiana.

121
00:06:55,420 --> 00:06:57,360
- We're not?
- No, we're going to California.

122
00:06:58,230 --> 00:06:59,740
Dad called from a pay phone

123
00:07:00,010 --> 00:07:01,130
Sacramento area code.

124
00:07:01,330 --> 00:07:02,300
Sam.

125
00:07:02,440 --> 00:07:05,820
Dean, if this demon killed mom and Jess and dad's closing in,

126
00:07:05,940 --> 00:07:08,040
we got to be there. We've got to help.

127
00:07:08,300 --> 00:07:09,420
Dad doesn't want our help.

128
00:07:09,450 --> 00:07:10,490
Well, I don't care.

129
00:07:10,840 --> 00:07:12,240
He's given us an order.

130
00:07:12,450 --> 00:07:13,770
I don't care.

131
00:07:15,340 --> 00:07:17,500
We don't always have to do what he says.

132
00:07:17,535 --> 00:07:18,230
Sam, dad is asking us to work jobs,

133
00:07:18,260 --> 00:07:19,930
