134
00:07:19,990 --> 00:07:22,250
All right, I understand. Believe me, I understand.

135
00:07:22,285 --> 00:07:24,510
But I'm talking one week here,
man, to get answers.

136
00:07:25,150 --> 00:07:26,430
To get revenge.

137
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:28,970
- All right, look, I know how you feel.
- Do you?

138
00:07:32,650 --> 00:07:34,100
How old were you when mom died,

139
00:07:34,250 --> 00:07:35,110
4?

140
00:07:35,990 --> 00:07:38,060
Jess died six months ago.

141
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:41,010
How the hell would you know how I feel?

142
00:07:42,390 --> 00:07:43,750
Dad said it wasn't safe

143
00:07:43,890 --> 00:07:45,140
