144
00:07:45,640 --> 00:07:47,470
He obviously knows something that we don't.

145
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:49,500
So if he says to stay away, we stay away.

146
00:07:49,510 --> 00:07:52,490
I don't understand the blind faith you have in the man.

147
00:07:53,260 --> 00:07:55,360
I mean, it's like you don't even question him.

148
00:07:55,470 --> 00:07:57,450
Yeah, it's called being a good son.

149
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:10,170
You're a selfish bastard. You know that?

150
00:08:11,100 --> 00:08:12,770
You just do whatever you want.

151
00:08:13,020 --> 00:08:14,870
You don't care what anybody thinks.

152
00:08:15,290 --> 00:08:17,240
- That's what you really think?
- Yes, it is.

153
00:08:19,280 --> 00:08:20,050
Well,

154
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:23,090
