156
00:08:26,950 --> 00:08:27,735
I am serious.

157
00:08:27,770 --> 00:08:29,140
It's the middle of the night.

158
00:08:29,410 --> 00:08:32,240
Hey, I'm taking off. I will leave your ass. You hear me!

159
00:08:35,990 --> 00:08:37,770
That's what I want you to do.

160
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:44,490
Goodbye, Sam.

161
00:09:54,420 --> 00:09:55,430
Let me guess.

162
00:09:55,590 --> 00:09:56,560
Scotty.

163
00:09:58,540 --> 00:09:59,290
Yep.

164
00:10:00,250 --> 00:10:01,880
Hi, my name is John Bonham.

165
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:04,100
Isn't that the drummer for Led Zeppelin?

166
00:10:05,380 --> 00:10:06,260
Wow.

167
00:10:06,560 --> 00:10:07,440
Good.

168
00:10:07,940 --> 00:10:09,500
Classic-rock fan.

169
00:10:09,930 --> 00:10:11,280
What can I do for you, John?

170
00:10:15,560 --> 00:10:16,810
I was wondering if...

171
00:10:17,090 --> 00:10:18,550
