172
00:10:22,090 --> 00:10:23,830
Nope. Who are they?

173
00:10:24,960 --> 00:10:25,930
Friends of mine.

174
00:10:25,970 --> 00:10:27,810
They went missing about a year ago.

175
00:10:28,100 --> 00:10:29,540
They passed through somewhere around here.

176
00:10:29,580 --> 00:10:31,490
