179
00:10:39,040 --> 00:10:41,920
Scotty, you got a smile that lights up a room.
Anybody ever tell you that?

180
00:10:46,700 --> 00:10:47,620
Never mind.

181
00:10:47,850 --> 00:10:48,780
See you around.

182
00:11:00,090 --> 00:11:01,190
Hey.

183
00:11:13,270 --> 00:11:15,120
You scared the hell out of me.

184
00:11:15,270 --> 00:11:18,160
I'm sorry. I just thought you might need some help.

185
00:11:19,640 --> 00:11:21,290
I'm good, thanks.

186
00:11:22,680 --> 00:11:24,420
Uh, so, where are you headed?

187
00:11:25,740 --> 00:11:28,180
No offense, but no way I'm telling you.

188
00:11:28,590 --> 00:11:29,420
