189
00:11:29,760 --> 00:11:31,690
You could be some kind of freak.

190
00:11:32,040 --> 00:11:33,200
I mean, you are hitchhiking.

191
00:11:33,550 --> 00:11:34,730
Well, so are you.

192
00:11:43,520 --> 00:11:44,460
Need a ride?

193
00:11:44,880 --> 00:11:45,810
- Yeah. Yeah.
- Yeah.

194
00:11:46,220 --> 00:11:47,190
Just her.

195
00:11:48,610 --> 00:11:49,870
I ain't taking you.

196
