You trust shady van guy and not me?

197
00:12:02,170 --> 00:12:03,520
Definitely.

198
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:13,280
You sure they didn't stop for gas or something?

199
00:12:14,620 --> 00:12:17,100
Nope, don't remember them.
You say they were friends of yours?

200
00:12:17,450 --> 00:12:18,330
That's right.

201
00:12:18,450 --> 00:12:20,010
Did the guy have a tattoo?

202
00:12:22,470 --> 00:12:23,680
Yes, he did.

203
00:12:27,130 --> 00:12:28,020
