216
00:15:13,570 --> 00:15:15,070
You still looking for your friends?

217
00:15:16,330 --> 00:15:18,190
You mind filling it up, there, Emily?

218
00:15:22,920 --> 00:15:24,730
So, did you grow up here?

219
