232
00:15:53,880 --> 00:15:55,460
Hey, you been out to the orchard?

233
00:15:55,640 --> 00:15:57,140
Seen that scarecrow?

234
00:15:58,380 --> 00:15:59,640
Yeah, it creeps me out.

235
00:16:00,460 --> 00:16:01,360
Whose is it?

236
00:16:01,500 --> 00:16:02,380
I don't know.

237
00:16:02,710 --> 00:16:03,930
It's just always been there.

238
00:16:05,380 --> 00:16:06,670
That your aunt and uncle's?

239
00:16:08,930 --> 00:16:09,820
Customer.

240
00:16:09,990 --> 00:16:11,160
