242
00:16:14,210 --> 00:16:15,010
Mm-hmm.

243
00:16:16,620 --> 00:16:19,140
Sorry, the Sacramento bus
doesn't run again till tomorrow.

244
00:16:19,930 --> 00:16:21,190
5:05 P.M.

245
00:16:21,360 --> 00:16:22,340
Tomorrow?

246
00:16:23,110 --> 00:16:24,160
There's got to be another way.

247
00:16:24,350 --> 00:16:25,180
Well, there is.

248
00:16:25,300 --> 00:16:26,310
Buy a car.

249
