Hey.

250
00:16:48,920 --> 00:16:49,750
Hey.

251
00:16:50,260 --> 00:16:51,310
You again.

252
00:16:51,930 --> 00:16:53,170
What happened to your ride?

253
00:16:53,920 --> 00:16:55,170
You were right.

254
00:16:55,370 --> 00:16:56,760
That guy was shady.

255
00:16:57,110 --> 00:16:58,320
