259
00:17:10,010 --> 00:17:11,130
No way.

260
00:17:11,320 --> 00:17:12,060
Yeah.

261
00:17:12,940 --> 00:17:13,810
Me, too.

262
00:17:16,280 --> 00:17:18,900
