275
00:17:43,865 --> 00:17:44,720
Oh, no.

276
00:17:45,080 --> 00:17:46,950
- Please.
- Nope, it's on the house.

277
00:17:48,690 --> 00:17:49,930
Hiya, Scotty.

278
00:17:51,360 --> 00:17:53,030
Can I get a coffee, black?

279
00:17:58,300 --> 00:17:58,940
