281
00:18:03,600 --> 00:18:04,620
How you doing?

282
00:18:04,740 --> 00:18:05,780
Just passing through?

283
00:18:05,840 --> 00:18:06,760
Road trip.

284
00:18:06,950 --> 00:18:07,720
Mmm.

285
00:18:08,920 --> 00:18:09,960
