316
00:19:24,850 --> 00:19:25,660
Yeah.

317
00:19:27,710 --> 00:19:29,250
You know, my brother could give you

318
00:19:29,350 --> 00:19:30,780
his puppy-dog look,

319
00:19:31,040 --> 00:19:32,630
and you'd just buy right into it.

320
00:19:34,410 --> 00:19:35,890
Thanks for coming, sheriff.

321
00:19:46,400 --> 00:19:47,750
I'd like a word, please.

322
00:19:48,920 --> 00:19:50,900
Come on. I'm having a bad day already.

323
00:19:53,790 --> 00:19:55,370
You don't want to make it worse.

324
00:20:13,110 --> 00:20:15,640
