360
00:22:55,175 --> 00:22:55,770
Don't ask.

361
00:23:01,290 --> 00:23:03,550
The scarecrow climbed off its cross?

362
00:23:04,030 --> 00:23:06,570
Hey, I'm telling you,
Burkitsville, Indiana, fun town.

363
00:23:07,530 --> 00:23:09,120
It didn't kill the couple, did it?

364
00:23:09,330 --> 00:23:10,040
No.

365
00:23:10,410 --> 00:23:12,130
I can cope without you, you know.

366
00:23:13,180 --> 00:23:15,510
