367
00:23:15,740 --> 00:23:16,800
No, it's more than a spirit.

368
00:23:16,860 --> 00:23:18,920
It's a god, a pagan god, anyway.

369
00:23:19,420 --> 00:23:20,560
What makes you say that?

370
00:23:21,030 --> 00:23:22,650
The annual cycle of its killings,

371
00:23:22,790 --> 00:23:24,560
and the fact that the victims are always a man and a woman,

372
00:23:24,640 --> 00:23:26,330
like some kind of fertility rite.

373
00:23:27,640 --> 00:23:29,090
And you should see the locals.

374
00:23:29,460 --> 00:23:30,640
The way they treated this couple

375
00:23:30,750 --> 00:23:32,660
