378
00:23:36,570 --> 00:23:39,450
Yeah, I'm thinking a ritual sacrifice
to appease some pagan god.

379
00:23:39,710 --> 00:23:41,860
So a god possesses the scarecrow...

380
00:23:41,940 --> 00:23:43,470
the scarecrow takes its sacrifice.

381
00:23:43,670 --> 00:23:44,680
And for another year,

382
00:23:44,720 --> 00:23:47,290
