457
00:27:32,230 --> 00:27:33,620
- Glad I could help.
- All right.

458
00:27:51,780 --> 00:27:53,260
You do understand, Harley?

459
00:27:53,940 --> 00:27:55,060
All of us here,

460
00:27:55,560 --> 00:27:57,780
