462
00:28:02,600 --> 00:28:03,720
better than all of you.

463
00:28:04,410 --> 00:28:05,940
I'm the one that gives them directions.

464
00:28:06,090 --> 00:28:08,000
I'm the one that sends them down to the orchard.

465
00:28:10,040 --> 00:28:11,690
Harley, please.

466
00:28:12,080 --> 00:28:13,190
We all close our doors,

467
00:28:14,160 --> 00:28:15,280
look the other way,

468
00:28:15,620 --> 00:28:17,390
pretend we can't hear the screams.

469
00:28:17,940 --> 00:28:19,290
But this is different.

470
00:28:19,620 --> 00:28:20,830
This is murder.

471
00:28:21,130 --> 00:28:22,380
It's angry with us.

472
00:28:23,580 --> 00:28:25,470
Already the trees are beginning to die.

473
00:28:26,540 --> 00:28:27,950
Tonight's the seventh night of the cycle,

474
00:28:28,200 --> 00:28:29,280
our last chance.

475
00:28:31,830 --> 00:28:33,260
If the boy has to die,

476
00:28:33,740 --> 00:28:35,030
the boy has to die.

477
00:28:36,390 --> 00:28:37,930
But why does it have to be her?

478
00:28:53,460 --> 00:28:54,720
Aunt Stacy...

479
00:28:55,060 --> 00:28:56,520
uncle Harley, please.

480
00:29:09,210 --> 00:29:10,750
Why are you doing this?

481
00:29:11,350 --> 00:29:12,550
For the common good.

482
00:29:18,800 --> 00:29:19,740
Hey.

483
00:29:20,230 --> 00:29:21,250
Our bus came in.

484
00:29:27,360 --> 00:29:28,530
You better catch it.

485
00:29:28,950 --> 00:29:29,950
I got to go.

486
00:29:30,510 --> 00:29:31,380
Go where?

487
00:29:32,590 --> 00:29:33,460
Burkitsville.

488
00:29:38,130 --> 00:29:38,900
Sam...

489
00:29:39,910 --> 00:29:40,710
wait.

490
00:29:41,450 --> 00:29:43,630
I've been trying to call my brother
for the last three hours.

491
00:29:44,040 --> 00:29:45,370
I'm just getting his voice mail.

492
00:29:45,630 --> 00:29:46,900
Maybe his phone is turned off.

493
00:29:47,020 --> 00:29:48,310
No, that's not like him.

494
00:29:50,810 --> 00:29:52,580
Meg, I think he might be in trouble.

495
00:29:53,070 --> 00:29:54,030
What kind of trouble?

496
00:29:54,130 --> 00:29:55,660
I can't really explain right now.

497
00:29:55,810 --> 00:29:57,780
I'm sorry.
Look, I don't want youto miss your bus.

498
00:29:57,830 --> 00:29:59,630
But I don't understand.

499
00:30:00,360 --> 00:30:02,020
You're running back to your brother?

500
00:30:03,370 --> 00:30:04,620
The guy you ran away from?

501
00:30:04,670 --> 00:30:06,910
Why, because he won't pick up his phone?

502
00:30:10,080 --> 00:30:10,860
Sam...

503
00:30:12,320 --> 00:30:13,120
come...

504
00:30:13,870 --> 00:30:15,280
