505
00:30:17,570 --> 00:30:18,490
I can't.

506
00:30:19,450 --> 00:30:20,320
I'm sorry.

507
00:30:21,740 --> 00:30:22,610
Why not?

508
00:30:23,900 --> 00:30:24,870
He's my family.

509
00:30:34,760 --> 00:30:35,920
I don't understand.

510
00:30:36,940 --> 00:30:38,260
They're gonna kill us?

511
00:30:42,850 --> 00:30:43,830
Sacrifice us...

512
00:30:44,630 --> 00:30:45,540
which is,

513
00:30:45,920 --> 00:30:47,330
