514
00:30:50,080 --> 00:30:51,820
You really didn't know anything about this...

515
00:30:53,700 --> 00:30:54,530
did you?

516
00:30:55,490 --> 00:30:56,350
About what?

517
00:30:57,000 --> 00:30:58,180
The scarecrow god?

518
00:31:00,000 --> 00:31:01,210
I can't believe this.

519
00:31:02,600 --> 00:31:03,860
Well, you better start believing,

520
00:31:04,230 --> 00:31:05,420
because I'm gonna need your help.

521
00:31:08,160 --> 00:31:08,880
Okay.

522
00:31:09,010 --> 00:31:09,810
Now,

523
00:31:10,380 --> 00:31:12,730
we can destroy the scarecrow,
but we got to find the tree.

524
00:31:12,940 --> 00:31:13,910
What tree?

525
00:31:14,240 --> 00:31:15,580
Maybe you can help me with that.

526
00:31:16,350 --> 00:31:17,390
It would be really old.

527
00:31:17,510 --> 00:31:19,100
The locals would treat it with a lot of respect,

528
00:31:19,390 --> 00:31:20,480
like it was sacred.

529
00:31:24,350 --> 00:31:26,240
There was this one apple tree.

530
00:31:26,660 --> 00:31:28,350
The immigrants brought it over with them.

531
00:31:28,650 --> 00:31:30,180
They call it"the first tree. "

532
00:31:30,420 --> 00:31:31,500
Is it in the orchard?

533
00:31:31,840 --> 00:31:32,480
Yeah,

534
00:31:32,680 --> 00:31:33,930
but I don't know where.

535
00:31:42,820 --> 00:31:43,770
It's time.

536
00:31:49,710 --> 00:31:51,450
